{"tid":2437863,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人考車肥左","createTime":"2021-03-08T06:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T10:14:03.000Z","uid":392026,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f87c8c92f66fb25f2131cdbff3e0a81ed6681dfc","tid":2437863,"uid":392026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:55:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hGXzwKYbQuo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhGXzwKYbQuo&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058priIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=070b7fed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hGXzwKYbQuo</a><br />\n<br />\n等左咁耐終於到考試 但唔合格<br />\n唔開心係好正常嘅😘但唔洗灰心💪🏻<br />\n我地會同大家分析下多數人肥D咩?🥺<br />\n又網上搵咗啲學神分享佢哋嘅故事🙈<br />\n之後同大家講下次點準備好<br />\n要申請補考定重考生快期？<br />\n希望幫到唔合格嘅人💪🏻💪🏻<br />\n考一次車真係好貴😌<br />\n有咩問題問我地都得嫁🙈🥰<br />\n我地答到一定答😎"},{"pid":"570ff4b4f487a791b215060aceb3dfc20d9b7bf0","tid":2437863,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"1take pass 冇機會重考 sor"},{"pid":"9842d217c4b2fa16f69c7b809a9f1cecb15aa7eb","tid":2437863,"uid":392026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"570ff4b4f487a791b215060aceb3dfc20d9b7bf0","tid":2437863,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"1take pass 冇機會重考 sor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:01:44.000Z","msg":"勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />恭喜晒"},{"pid":"e99c19fed61cacd9945d34398443a7fd383b68ee","tid":2437863,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"好溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f7ee38a1c6f957dade837736e5e3a14b554851","tid":2437863,"uid":231054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:06:59.000Z","msg":"星期五考天光道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等左兩年好驚肥<img src=\"/assets/face